- Will cost about a baseline price of 15k.<br>
- Cannot swim underwater.<br>
- Cannot move while fighting/casting (You'll probably need to dismount to chase something if it runs, as some Melee classes at least).<br>
- Take a short, but significant amount of time to stop from full speed to standing and from standing to full speed.<br>
- Are unsummoned when dismounted.<br>
- Are summoned by a Horse whistle which is soulbound.<br>
- Can only be used outdoors.<br>
- Will run slightly slower than SoW.<br>
- Skills may be limited on the horse (Imagine doing a Flying Kick on a horse).<br>
- They cannot be attacked.<br>
- They do not protect you from any spells (If you're rooted, you can't move).<br>
<br>
Basically, they're a luxury item. Something to use to look cool.<br>
<br>
This list of features came from a CGW mag review. Verant is still developing SoL and this isn't completely finished yet, so these features may change.<br>
